Insider Activity


Individual




Richard Kevin Hardage



Mr. Richard K. Hardage is Independent Director at HollyFrontier Corp., Chief Executive Officer at Turtle Creek Trust Co., Managing Partner at TCTC Holdings LLC and Co-Founder, President & Portfolio Manager at Turtle Creek Management LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at HollyFrontier Corp. He also serves as Chief Executive Officer of Turtle Creek Trust Company, LTA. Prior to co-founding Turtle Creek Management in 2006, from 1998 to 2002 he served as Vice President of Brown Brothers Harriman & Co. and manager of the firm's Dallas office. From 2002 to 2006 he served as a Vice President of U.S. Trust Company, N.A. and portfolio manager.
Mr. Hardage is a graduate of the University of Texas at Austin, having earned a Bachelor of Arts degree from the College of Liberal Arts in 1983, and an M.B.A. from the Graduate School of Business in 1986. He received a J.D. degree from Southern Methodist University School of Law in 1989.



